Text.string: Oh, hey. It's you again.
Welcome in. There's no Wi-Fi.
Welcome to the grind, brah.
Holler atcha!
Oh, nice, hey again! I've always wanted a regular.
You're looking at the galaxy record holder for longest pourover. Two and a half months, brah. I think the customer, like, died waiting at the pickup counter.
I was at the gym earlier. Just needed everyone to know that.
What if I'm, like, just a collection of circuits and electrons? Whoa.
When you really think about it, it's all about the beans. All of it.
Just another day of doin' what I love. If only these customers didn't keep showing up.
Did you, uh, want some coffee or whatever?
Welcome to our humble establishment. We hope you have a good day, I guess.
Whoa! Gettin' some serious vibe energy from this direction.
I'm on break. Workin' on my screenplay. I'm in the zone. You'll have to come back later.
You might want to work on this whole look you've got goin' there.
Did you know some people are from other planets? It's true. Got some ECHOtube vids I could send you.
Are you a talent agent? I've been waiting to get discovered!
Had to come get a hot brew? I know the feel, brah.
How's it hoverin'?
We're a non-dairy, non-vegetable, non-liquid establishment, so I can only whisper the word “milk” softly into your cup.
Thanks for vibin' it and keepin' it tight. If you need me, I'm on my ECHO.
Have a roasty day!
Thanks for hangin' out.
Later.
See you next time, brah!
